text: Willem King gret Edmund mine scirrefe, and Alfwine Gottune, and Leofwine scune freondlice.

And icc kythe eow that icc wille that se theriden tha land at Wattone and att Dakkewrd Sainte Petre to hande and me into Westminstre swa full and swa forth swa hi firmest thder inne lathan and seceth Ã¦fter mine rihte tha icc tharafter mid rihte ah to habbene be mine fullen frendsipe that nan other ne sy.
